<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In order to unify Zend's class APIs, I'd propose to rename {{Zend_Config::asArray()}} to {{Zend_Config::toArray()}}. This would match the names of the methods in Zend_Db_Table (row) and Zend_Console_Getopt.</p>

    </div>
